Using Selenium to test grails app which uses ZK Framework

Grails app testing with selenium
http://www.grails.org/plugin/selenium


ZK app testing with selenium and Junit
http://docs.zkoss.org/wiki/ZK_Unit_Testing
http://docs.zkoss.org/wiki/How_to_Test_ZK_Application_with_Selenium


This project aims to tell you how to combine both and test grails+zk using selenium.